Visualize the outliers identified by each method

Source: R/ggoutliers.R
plot-datacleaner-ANY-method.Rd

Visualize the outliers identified by each method

Usage

# S4 method for class 'datacleaner,ANY'
plot(x, y, raw = TRUE)

Arguments

x

. the datacleaner object

y

. the species index or name for multiple species

raw

Whether total number of outlier flagged in each method are provided (TRUE) or FALSE to return the percentage outlier contribution for each method.

Value

ggplot object indicating outlier detection methods and number of outlier flagged.
